+     - string
+     - Hash algorithm name, e.g. ``"sha256"``.
    * - ``data-block-size``
      - u32
      - Data block size in bytes (>= 512, typically 4096).
    * - ``hash-block-size``
      - u32
      - Hash block size in bytes (>= 512, typically 4096).
